{"tid":439632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18/10 教大女生中招 被呃28萬港元","createTime":"2017-10-18T03:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T03:41:29.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bebd52ff7e7ea6d7c1e0d2cce49c3d7096e2e518","tid":439632,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:29:35.000Z","msg":"昨晚9時許，大埔露屏路香港教育大學，一名姓田22歲內地女生報案指，於本月12日接獲一名不明男子來電，對方自稱為速遞公司職員，指她一個包裹涉嫌與一宗刑事案件有關，她遂向該名男子提供其個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n女事主其後再收到一名自稱是內地執法人員的男子來電，並要求她將約28萬元港幣存入一個內地戶口。她按指示存款後懷疑受騙，於是報案。經初步調查，案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，交由大埔警區刑事調查第七隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57345447&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57345447%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171018&d=u3ii42TOxFjH6%2FPSemRc4zOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=8b9f03ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57345447%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171018&h=e78f02d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57345447&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171018</a>"},{"pid":"4714af02c88e5c72f814ee18798ef66f0eb2c339","tid":439632,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e15782d9744c383ab212d2367ea10c12dacd6dd","tid":439632,"uid":48092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:33:44.000Z","msg":"呃返自己人就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336913b76a64d2b952d81af87fc18341556b6125","tid":439632,"uid":34167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:36:37.000Z","msg":"係d NDS先咁柒蠢"},{"pid":"f8f5b2dd04d4954aa50abc52945c2595f7e9